					<div class="areaText">
						<h4>Study Area</h4>
						<p>The study defined here is roughly 13 km<sup>2</sup>. We designed our sampling campaign to measure within these bounds in order to: <br>1. Maintain our sampling density - to ensure we cover nearly all the navigable roads in a 3.5 hour time window. <br> 2. Utilize external datasets - to cross-validate our calculated emissions with existing CO<sub>2</sub> emissions inventories that were provided for this study area.

						</p>

